Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我好友的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是何时开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,一直压抑着情感过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.17,0:00:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我和好友敦\N从以前就感情很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也觉得在今后\N仍然一直是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不过已经回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我对他的女友...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢上了他的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,（明明是好友的女友）\N（却表现出喜欢我的样子）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.35,0:01:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,（于是在好友去旅行时）\N（我骑上她干个不停）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还要再一会呢\N再等我准备一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再一会就好了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,敦 再撑一会吧\N我的肚子已经很不争气了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么回事啊?\N感觉在滚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,来了呢，就要这个\N真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:02:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这点酒还可以吗?\N这样一个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么自己倒?\N没差啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那么就差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去了呢\N在倒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?\N可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉滚超大的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来咯 干杯\N开喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都出了社会\N现在有着各自的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,敦在广告公司工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他的女友祥子，是事务所OL
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我则是求职中的尼特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,敦和祥子\N是大学时就交往的情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们交往差不多...三年了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.06,0:03:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,而且好友的我\N则也在那时候 认识了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我和敦总会谈上许多事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有工作的事，或是读书时的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.54,0:03:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,儿时玩伴的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就算走上的道路不同\N但是仍然是好友
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.15,0:03:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候可真是认真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要是没变的话呢?\N也许现在是警察了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小时候可是很向往的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.11,0:04:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,倒是别看他这样\N他小时候很小只的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真可怜，被欺压了吧?\N所以那时总是都嗨不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.79,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念呢\N倒是敦啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.93,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,许久未见的我们\N聊到都忘了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,后来等到察觉时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不太会喝酒的敦\N已经不知不觉睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.48,0:04:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,于是我和好友的女友\N就这么两个人独处了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.96,0:05:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,敦睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太久没见所以太开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不过一下就睡觉呢\N真的不会喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,也太弱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来\N现在没有末班车了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们怎么办？住下来?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢\N敦倒是先睡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃\N真的很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呢\N还想再吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不过已经喝多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然刚刚问过了\N聪真的没有女友?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就没有咯\N为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然问为什么啊...\N有些邂逅吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有呢\N是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是尼特啊\N会参加饮酒会吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,把敦的吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.22,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得一开始认识时吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,其实喜欢的不是敦\N而是觉得聪比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的哦\N突然说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要开奇怪的玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我反是羡慕你们两个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？只有羡慕?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是羡慕敦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,羡慕敦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么羡慕敦啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子，怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很奇怪啊\N你流汗了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,只是摸手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.90,0:09:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是没错啦，但...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉很怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪啊\N怪？怪什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太近？不喜欢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是不喜欢，但是敦...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不行？不喜欢?\N没不喜欢，但是敦在不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，他在睡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子，敦在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,放心，他醉倒不会醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N你说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是吗?\N这么怕被发现?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,敦，没事吧？睡好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.36,0:15:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.23,0:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,在敦去员工旅行时
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,祥子来到了我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.44,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,天气真好\N只是有点凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,会冷啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啊?\N好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好热啊\N变热了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是个不可思议的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,身为好友女友的祥子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正在我的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,前几天她说一直都喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不过他是好友的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是无法背叛好友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然而...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,超有趣的\N真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好热啊\N好热吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.63,0:21:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,想要啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.21,0:23:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌，害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.48,0:25:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.75,0:26:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要去床上吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.53,0:27:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么舔腋下?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.20,0:27:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞吗?\N害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.47,0:28:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦\N超喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.56,0:28:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一直舔腋下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.86,0:29:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.53,0:29:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.86,0:30:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这里好赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.04,0:30:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.77,0:31:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗?\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.21,0:32:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.48,0:32:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以舔吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.33,0:33:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,热吗?\N好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.60,0:33:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.32,0:34:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,实在好爽\N是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.88,0:34:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.40,0:37:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可以插入吗?\N可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.81,0:37:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？直接插入?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.15,0:37:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?\N进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.16,0:37:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还是上套好了\N套子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.83,0:37:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.71,0:37:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.18,0:37:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然一直摸\N等等
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.94,0:38:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快插入了，可以吗？\N不想吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.44,0:38:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了，好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.78,0:38:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.72,0:39:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.86,0:40:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.73,0:40:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.63,0:40:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.23,0:40:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.73,0:42:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.13,0:42:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.99,0:43:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.89,0:43:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.04,0:44:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.46,0:44:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.62,0:45:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞\N实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.79,0:45:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.78,0:46:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.86,0:46:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.47,0:47:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.27,0:47:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了呢\N是啊，看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.03,0:47:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.72,0:47:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.13,0:48:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,都是汗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.47,0:48:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.89,0:48:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.83,0:48:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,实在受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.26,0:49:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.99,0:50:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.54,0:50:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.24,0:50:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.94,0:51:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.99,0:52:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.42,0:52:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽\N再多插一点
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.96,0:53:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗？\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.98,0:53:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.41,0:53:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,去了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.55,0:53:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗?\N实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.61,0:54:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.75,0:55:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,要不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.43,0:55:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.71,0:56:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.86,0:56:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了，可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.46,0:57:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.54,0:57:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.43,0:57:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞\N射了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.91,0:57:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,射得真多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.24,0:57:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.38,0:57:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.26,0:58:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.73,0:58:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N不行了?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.11,0:59:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多呢\N是啊 等我拿面纸
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.05,0:59:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,面纸吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.60,0:59:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,超多的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.47,0:59:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.89,0:59:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.96,0:59:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.63,0:59:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思，实在好爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.17,0:59:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，好爽呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.65,1:00:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去冲澡吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.06,1:00:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.67,1:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.28,1:00:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,超多泡泡的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.48,1:00:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,想不到这么多
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.55,1:00:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沾到了呢\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.36,1:00:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不错吧\N真舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.05,1:01:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.06,1:01:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗?\N可以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.53,1:01:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞\N真行
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.14,1:01:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好强
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.21,1:01:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好会吹
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.15,1:01:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喷到了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.02,1:01:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,跑到眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.29,1:01:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好难啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.76,1:02:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你真会吹呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.17,1:02:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.24,1:02:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽呢\N是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.59,1:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都是泡泡哦，这里都是呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.61,1:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又沾到了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.22,1:03:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,泡泡都消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.52,1:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:47.27,1:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽\N这么泡着真赞呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.02,1:04:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,吹一下\N破了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.49,1:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.69,1:04:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,吹慢一点
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.16,1:04:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好难啊，你刚刚真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.77,1:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,完全没办法
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.60,1:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要喝什么好呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.54,1:04:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,就选喜欢的嘛...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.21,1:05:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,苹果汁好了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.17,1:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.64,1:05:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么？你不喝吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.66,1:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不要吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.07,1:06:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝\N真甜
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.34,1:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.65,1:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如何？好了吗?\N再一会
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.32,1:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来真好吃\N要吃很多菜吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.72,1:06:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,要很多哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.19,1:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可以抱着吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.33,1:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要很多哦\N会加进去的
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.13,1:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，很危险啊\N危险吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.07,1:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N很危险，别乱动
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.68,1:07:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.28,1:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.02,1:07:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.16,1:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要吃拉面了?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.90,1:07:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃了对吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.38,1:07:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一会再说，等等啦
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.78,1:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你做什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.20,1:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要可以了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.74,1:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很危险，煮好了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.21,1:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃吗?\N要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.88,1:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.55,1:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是要吃吗？煮好了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.29,1:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要脱?\N别管为什么了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.96,1:08:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,会糊掉啦\N会吃啦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.77,1:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吗？很烫哦，\N这样子可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.24,1:08:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,做什么啊？很危险，这很烫的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.72,1:09:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.99,1:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很危险 很烫的\N很烫吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.53,1:09:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,很烫吗?\N好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.80,1:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？那一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.81,1:09:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.75,1:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么脱呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.95,1:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.23,1:09:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.63,1:09:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好了嘛\N是啊，但为什么要脱?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.78,1:10:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来好好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.18,1:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.73,1:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是拉面味呢\N没有哦
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.01,1:10:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗?\N好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.95,1:10:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好热了呢\N是啊，好热呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.84,1:11:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗?\N来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.64,1:11:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,会烫吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.98,1:11:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题，好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.73,1:11:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样味道可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.47,1:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还要吃吗？还有哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.94,1:11:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吃吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.35,1:11:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,再吃一点吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.84,1:12:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她什么都没说\N就再次来到我家
Dialogue: 0,1:12:24.05,1:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有着彷佛是情侣般的错觉
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.53,1:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,过着幸福的时刻
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.68,1:15:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.67,1:16:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这里吧
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.69,1:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽，再多来一点
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.58,1:19:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.45,1:19:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.07,1:19:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.22,1:19:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽，好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.03,1:19:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.04,1:20:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.12,1:20:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞，实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.98,1:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.88,1:21:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.83,1:22:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，才刚去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.53,1:22:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.83,1:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.00,1:25:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.58,1:25:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽\N不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.53,1:25:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.86,1:27:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.16,1:27:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.35,1:28:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.96,1:28:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.57,1:28:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.99,1:29:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.38,1:30:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.19,1:30:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.07,1:30:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.17,1:32:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.18,1:34:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.73,1:34:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.88,1:35:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.49,1:35:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.36,1:35:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N要去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.64,1:36:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:36:58.65,1:37:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.61,1:37:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙了\N受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.29,1:37:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽，不妙，要射了\N要不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.97,1:37:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了，实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.64,1:37:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:31.19,1:41:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.41,1:41:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,早安\N太早了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.34,1:41:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.37,1:42:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还想睡吗?\N想睡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.64,1:42:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.42,1:43:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,起来了?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.86,1:43:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要拍?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:50.53,1:43:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.20,1:43:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？为什么要拍?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.81,1:44:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞吗？\N讨厌啦，害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.08,1:44:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,拍的不错哦\N讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.29,1:44:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.50,1:44:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一直拍啊\N没关系的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:30.97,1:44:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.31,1:44:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,才刚起床就这么?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.56,1:45:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了了吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.77,1:45:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,看得到吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:16.81,1:46:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.89,1:46:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真淫荡
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.14,1:47:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.43,1:47:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.31,1:47:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.85,1:48:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.26,1:48:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.56,1:48:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:54.70,1:48:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,1:49:06.84,1:49:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多啊
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.60,1:49:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,痒吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:39.14,1:49:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多呢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.31,1:50:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.72,1:50:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.66,1:50:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，都是精液\N不喜欢?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.01,1:50:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还要再多做一点哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:43.59,1:52:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,敦快要旅行回来了
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.27,1:52:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只剩一晚的自由
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.95,1:53:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好想时间就这么停下来
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.55,1:53:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,有生以来第一次这么想的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.76,1:53:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这个想法不只是我
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.57,1:53:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想必祥子也是\N有着和我一样的想法
Dialogue: 0,1:53:38.45,1:53:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然而时间并不会停止
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.66,1:53:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以直到敦回来...\N直到快没有时间为止...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:54.20,1:53:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们确实而充分地相爱
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.09,2:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情摸吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:10.88,2:03:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.16,2:04:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有爽吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:27.94,2:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了，能插入了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.68,2:07:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可以插入了吧?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.76,2:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,来插吧
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.77,2:08:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好赞
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.90,2:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽 祥子\N我也好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.71,2:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.47,2:09:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行了 好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:10:55.48,2:10:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?\N好喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.69,2:11:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.49,2:11:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好喜欢 好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,2:11:13.77,2:11:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.70,2:11:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:11:57.81,2:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.98,2:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:12:49.46,2:12:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吗?\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:13:24.70,2:13:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:13:27.36,2:13:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有很爽吗?\N好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.62,2:16:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.77,2:16:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,东西送人了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:08.65,2:17:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,实在好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.86,2:17:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那里不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.07,2:17:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,插那里要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:43.49,2:17:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，现在不行
Dialogue: 0,2:17:48.82,2:17:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,住手，现在不行
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.70,2:18:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，才刚去啊
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.31,2:18:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.22,2:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.16,2:20:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.44,2:20:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:21:18.77,2:21:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，好喜欢你\N我也喜欢啊
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.28,2:22:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，那里好爽
Dialogue: 0,2:23:22.49,2:23:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:23:26.49,2:23:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:23:39.44,2:23:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射嘴吗？要射了
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.09,2:24:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,又射好多了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:24:43.24,2:24:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,全部射出来了吗?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:37.75,2:26:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不好接吗？抱歉
Dialogue: 0,2:26:42.16,2:26:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,打过去咯\N来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:26:47.49,2:26:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,完全看不到 太久没打了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:26:52.83,2:26:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很久了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:26:55.50,2:26:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了\N真行呢
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.18,2:27:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,后来又过了一段时间
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.52,2:27:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,员工旅行回来的敦\N和女友还是一样过的幸福
Dialogue: 0,2:27:24.46,2:27:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,而我和祥子的关系
Dialogue: 0,2:27:30.47,2:27:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,从那天以来\N就像是一开始一样
Dialogue: 0,2:27:36.61,2:27:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕不会再有第二次了
Dialogue: 0,2:27:43.02,2:27:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我好友的女友...
Dialogue: 0,2:27:51.16,2:27:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,还是躲不过吗?\N等等，要被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:00.10,2:28:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是差一点，等等啦
Dialogue: 0,2:28:05.44,2:28:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的...
Dialogue: 0,2:28:09.44,2:28:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真是累死了
Dialogue: 0,2:28:16.38,2:28:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？\N你体力也太好了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:28:20.92,2:28:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有点累，休息一下\N好啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:23.99,2:28:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,先放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,2:28:33.87,2:28:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候她会有所行动
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.59,2:29:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候的回忆...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:47.01,2:29:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就算现在也无法忘记...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:53.56,2:30:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,（98堂Artist）
